moji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03fc5a14d9b71e9ee5ddf971a6de8aa7baa4401a","tid":138711,"uid":70527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T21:59:15.000Z","msg":"仲有既係佢地都變左啦"},{"pid":"57003eca8ac1a19f6765bcdb17d03c61b4e5ff38","tid":138711,"uid":17214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T22:01:26.000Z","msg":"已經唔知幾耐無試過成班朋友一齊食野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，經過M記見到啲學生一齊起哄嘅時候，就好羨慕佢地依然可以成班friend一齊玩一齊笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae72558147191f19e96639afbcdfcf1fa2db54ad","tid":138711,"uid":17767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T22:21:26.000Z","msg":"前日渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我上一個係1月1號"},{"pid":"eaf57ace54ca8a761040b55594e14dbe5d6a9024","tid":138711,"uid":28256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T22:24:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可能自己個人太念舊，就算大家各散東西有新圈子，都好想約翻埋啲朋友岀黎見下面，明明知道已經無咩可能，始終讀書嘅讀書，翻工嘅翻工，個個都難就時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好念舊,岩岩個夢仲要係中學新學期開學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 見番好多人"},{"pid":"ea54ba93ac293324597ac064b979130878182ab9","tid":138711,"uid":67878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T18:35:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}